						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the wall to the right of the main entrance of the Chintalarāya temple.</p>						

						<p>Records the homage of Pōtarāja-Liṁgarāja, son of Pōtarāja Yallamarāja of Tāḍiparti to the god Chintalarāya. In characters of about the 17th century A.D.</p>						

